类 RelMdDistribution

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.rel.metadata.RelMdDistribution
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    MetadataHandler<BuiltInMetadata.Distribution>

    public class RelMdDistribution
extends Object
implements MetadataHandler<BuiltInMetadata.Distribution>
    RelMdCollation supplies a default implementation of RelMetadataQuery.distribution(org.apache.calcite.rel.RelNode) for the standard logical algebra.
